🔍 AWS Error-Explainer Questions


!explain RequestLimitExceeded: Request limit exceeded. (EC2)
!explain ThrottlingException: Rate exceeded on DynamoDB
!explain InvalidGroupId.NotFound: The security group 'sg-12345' does not exist
!explain BucketAlreadyExists: The requested bucket name is not available
!explain InvalidAMIID.NotFound: ami-0abcdef1234567890
!explain SubnetNotFound: subnet-12345
!explain UnauthorizedOperation: You are not authorized to perform this operation
!explain SnapshotCreationPerVolumeRateExceeded
!explain ECS service (service my-service) is unable to place tasks
!explain Lambda: InvalidParameterValueException - Error occurred while GetObject. S3 Error Code: NoSuchKey


🏗️ Infrastructure Design (Natural → Terraform)

!generate terraform Create a VPC with 2 public subnets, 2 private subnets, NAT gateways, and an Internet gateway across us-east-1a and us-east-1b
!generate terraform An S3 bucket with versioning, AES-256 encryption, and a lifecycle rule to move objects to Glacier after 30 days
!generate terraform A Lambda function triggered by an S3 PUT event, with IAM role and CloudWatch logs
!generate terraform An Auto Scaling Group of t3.micro EC2s behind an Application Load Balancer, using a launch template
!generate terraform A DynamoDB table with on-demand billing, point-in-time recovery, and a GS



📊 Log / Metric Prompts (for when we add !analyze logs)


!analyze logs /aws/lambda/production-api 1
