Ask these live in interviews—easy 30-second demo:
“Why did my AMI disappear?” → !explain InvalidAMIID.NotFound
“What’s rate-limiting in AWS?” → !explain ThrottlingException
“Generate secure S3 boilerplate” → !generate terraform encrypted S3 bucket with KMS



Temperature Tip:

0.0 → Very deterministic (factual, repetitive)
0.2 → Best for code and precise answers
0.3 → Balanced and concise
0.7+ → More creative, but can drift off-topic